General.Name: Advanced Connection Technology
General.Description: Advanced Connection Technology Inc. engages in the design, manufacture, and sale of connectors and cable assemblies in Taiwan. Its connector products include USB type C, USB, HDMI, USCAR, OBD, and battery connectors; and cable products comprise USB type C, USB, HDMI, USCAR, OBD, vehicle, din, power, RCA, and coaxial cables. The company also provides modules; internal, external, and car antennas; portable electrical outlets; and LVDS, PCBA, and power chargers. It serves the automotive, consumer electronics, medical, and aerospace industries. The company was founded in 1994 and is headquartered in New Taipei City, Taiwan.
